{"tid":1480884,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"呢2條文宣片睇到我打哂冷震","createTime":"2019-08-17T13:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:52:21.000Z","uid":76743,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"faaca881638b65345c1d00ce378d7198dd172edf","tid":1480884,"uid":76743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zXA6-gBmqes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzXA6-gBmqes&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=c8ff5089\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zXA6-gBmqes</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YSUtmDHOIPI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYSUtmDHOIPI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=af70f422\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YSUtmDHOIPI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n開頭諗住都係d普通片有人Forward咪睇下囉<br />\n睇完不得不佩服剪片同搵料既義士心機<br />\n有時勇武做左幾多野 受左幾多傷<br />\n真係得現場既人先知道<br />\n係屋企或者番緊工既真係唔知咁多<br />\n勇武為殺出條血路<br />\n和理非係條路攦種子令到滿地開花<br />\n雖然香港而家係亂世<br />\n但我居然有一刻見到自己城市既人<br />\n可以為左公義企到咁埋咁齊心而感動<br />\n以往雨傘唔夠1個月就又打牌又燒野食<br />\n<br />\n學古美門咁講&quot;你了解左戰鬥既意義未?&quot;<br />\n今年2019既我地真係已經準備好戰鬥<br />\n不論文戰武戰 真係 &quot;五大訴求 缺一不可&quot;<br />\n<br />\n睇睇下條片 有個女人講左句<br />\n100萬 200萬 馬路又佔過 不合作又做左 工又罷過<br />\n生命都殤落過 點解可以咁殘忍完全無回應<br />\n我聽到呢一句我真係流左眼淚<br />\n<br />\n感動既係大家既團結<br />\n悲傷既係政府既暴政<br />\n<br />\n呢行眼淚 後面既感情真係好復雜...<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"0b6eb4536ea6760a1794bb5c9237e956ec700324","tid":1480884,"uid":162541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"推，第二條片好正，但第一次睇"},{"pid":"a3f6ec90147c07adc16732449baa42121d186278","tid":1480884,"uid":252292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:52:21.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"}]}